[9.311093, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1mрҹ’Ў Key Takeaway\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[9.311116, "o", "   Aperture does NOT change what tools Composio exposes.\r\n"]
[9.311195, "o", "   Aperture does NOT change what the agent decides to do.\r\n"]
[9.311236, "o", "   Aperture ONLY optimizes HOW tool results are delivered to the LLM.\r\n"]
[9.311299, "o", "   It's a compression + caching + token-counting layer on top of Composio.\r\n"]
